    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [900ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once slightly browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
