        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the<strong> remaining ciabatta[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced ciabatta</strong> to a<strong> toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once warmed through, spread a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong>, then cut each half into triangles – this is your <strong>ciabatta toast</strong></p>",
