    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Italian-style bean, tomato & greens stew</strong> with the <strong>ciabatta toast</strong> on the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
